### ============================================================================
### CORRIDA TRAINING SYSTEM - TEST REQUESTS
### ============================================================================
### Use a extensão "REST Client" do VS Code para executar estes testes
### Clique em "Send Request" acima de cada requisição
### ============================================================================

### 1. HEALTH CHECK
### Verificar se a API está respondendo
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### ============================================================================

### 2. REGISTRAR EDUCADOR
### Criar um novo educador
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "educador@example.com",
  "password": "SenhaSegura123",
  "name": "João Educador",
  "type": "educator"
}

### ============================================================================

### 3. REGISTRAR ALUNO
### Criar um novo aluno
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "aluno@example.com",
  "password": "SenhaSegura123",
  "name": "Maria Aluna",
  "type": "student"
}

### ============================================================================

### 4. LOGIN EDUCADOR
### Fazer login com educador
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "educador@example.com",
  "password": "SenhaSegura123"
}

### ============================================================================

### 5. LOGIN ALUNO
### Fazer login com aluno
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "aluno@example.com",
  "password": "SenhaSegura123"
}

### ============================================================================

### 6. OBTER DADOS DO USUÁRIO (EDUCADOR)
### Substitua o token abaixo pelo token retornado do login/register
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOiJjbHJzOXdyZjAwMDAwMDAwMDAwMDAwMDEiLCJlbWFpbCI6ImVkdWNhZG9yQGV4YW1wbGUuY29tIiwidHlwZSI6ImVkdWNhdG9yIiwiaWF0IjoxNjc0OTk5OTk5LCJleHAiOjE2NzU2MDQ3OTl9.XXXX

### ============================================================================

### 7. OBTER DADOS DO USUÁRIO (ALUNO)
### Substitua o token abaixo pelo token retornado do login/register
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOiJjbHJzOXdyZjAwMDAwMDAwMDAwMDAwMDIiLCJlbWFpbCI6ImFsdW5vQGV4YW1wbGUuY29tIiwidHlwZSI6InN0dWRlbnQiLCJpYXQiOjE2NzQ5OTk5OTksImV4cCI6MTY3NTYwNDc5OX0.XXXX

### ============================================================================

### 8. LOGOUT
### Fazer logout
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOiJjbHJzOXdyZjAwMDAwMDAwMDAwMDAwMDEiLCJlbWFpbCI6ImVkdWNhZG9yQGV4YW1wbGUuY29tIiwidHlwZSI6ImVkdWNhdG9yIiwiaWF0IjoxNjc0OTk5OTk5LCJleHAiOjE2NzU2MDQ3OTl9.XXXX

### ============================================================================

### 9. ERRO: LOGIN COM SENHA INCORRETA
### Testar validação de erro
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "educador@example.com",
  "password": "SenhaErrada"
}

### ============================================================================

### 10. ERRO: ACESSAR ROTA PROTEGIDA SEM TOKEN
### Testar autenticação obrigatória
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/me

### ============================================================================

### 11. ERRO: REGISTRAR COM EMAIL INVÁLIDO
### Testar validação de email
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "email-invalido",
  "password": "SenhaSegura123",
  "name": "Test User",
  "type": "educator"
}

### ============================================================================

### 12. ERRO: REGISTRAR COM SENHA CURTA
### Testar validação de senha
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "123",
  "name": "Test User",
  "type": "educator"
}

### ============================================================================

### 13. ERRO: REGISTRAR COM TIPO INVÁLIDO
### Testar validação de tipo
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "SenhaSegura123",
  "name": "Test User",
  "type": "invalid"
}

### ============================================================================

### INSTRUÇÕES:
### 1. Instale a extensão "REST Client" no VS Code
### 2. Abra este arquivo (test.http)
### 3. Clique em "Send Request" acima de cada teste
### 4. Veja a resposta no painel "Response"
### 5. Copie tokens das respostas e cole nos testes que precisam
### 6. Teste os erros para validar as mensagens

### ============================================================================
